{
  "stem": "24195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- he was taunting us all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was telling us, yeah, you guys are OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're doing-- but it doesn't matter how good a job you do, because you're not going to live long to enjoy all these-- all these things.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're not-- your days are counted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everyday he'd come to us, and we would just look at him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no sense in getting into an argument with him, because anybody who would get in an argument, he'd be hauled off like that and have to go with them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we didn't say anything, but he came every day and did the same spiel over and over again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It doesn't-- it doesn't count.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It doesn't matter how good you are.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you do all your work, down to the-- to the letter, in the end, you're going to be executed regardless.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that's what the long range plans are for people like you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every one of those steps would only be against us, would prolong the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that would possibly put us at risks that we'd never--never survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was-- nobody really said anything about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it became a routine of work every day that people appeared to be either dumb, acting dumb, or clumsy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was an organized-- a very orchestrated effort to undermine the-- the work and the building of that airfield, and doing everything with them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I mean, I remember one day an army truck came, and they had a giant roll with those telephone cables on there, like you see on those extra large-- I don't know what you call these-- wheels, cables.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were as supposed to string it out, take it off the truck, and string it.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
